ency\nresponse was generated for a series of simulations in the cantilever beam\ninvolving different damage scenarios. This case study shows the effectiveness\nof the above approaches to predict bending rigidity with an acceptable error\nrate.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sat, 17 Aug 2019 17:47:24 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-08-20"}
